---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Terms of Use" isStatic={true}>
    <main class="static-page-container">
        <h1 class="static-title font-baumans">Terms of Use</h1>
        
        <div class="legal-content">
            <section>
                <p>
                    By entering the <span class="font-baumans"><span class="flip-b">B</span>eBulbed</span> 
                    environment, you agree to engage with our research and ideas under the following 
                    Laboratory Protocols. This space is dedicated to the world we want to see, and 
                    your participation should reflect that intent.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="legal-heading">1. Laboratory Access</h2>
                <p>
                    This website is a digital extension of our research laboratory. Access is granted 
                    for personal, non-commercial exploration of our concepts and designs. Any 
                    unauthorized attempt to disrupt the stability of this environment is strictly 
                    prohibited.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="legal-heading">2. Intellectual Boundaries</h2>
                <p>
                    The concepts, designs, and sparks of ideas found here are the intellectual 
                    property of <span class="font-baumans"><span class="flip-b">B</span>eBulbed</span>. 
                    You are encouraged to be inspired by them, but you may not claim, redistribute, 
                    or monetize our research without explicit written permission.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="legal-heading">3. Experimental Nature</h2>
                <p>
                    Because the world isn’t finished yet, our work is in a constant state of 
                    evolution. Everything presented here is "experimental." We provide this 
                    information on an "as-is" basis and make no warranties regarding the 
                    completeness or permanence of any specific project or idea.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="legal-heading">4. Protocol Evolution</h2>
                <p>
                    Our protocols may change as our research moves forward. By continuing to 
                    access the lab, you accept the current version of these terms. We recommend 
                    checking this space occasionally to stay aligned with our evolving standards.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .legal-content {
        max-width: 750px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px; 
        color: var(--zinc-text);
        line-height: 1.7; 
        font-weight: 300;
        padding-bottom: 10vh;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        
        /* --- NEW ALIGNMENT --- */
        text-align: justify;
        text-justify: inter-word; /* Ensures even distribution of space */
    }

    /* --- MOBILE RESPONSIVENESS --- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .static-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .legal-content {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0 20px;
            /* Optional: If justified looks too "gappy" on very small phones, 
               you can switch it back to left on mobile only, but usually 
               justify looks fine with inter-word. */
            text-align: justify; 
        }

        .legal-heading {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 32px; 
    }

    .legal-heading {
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 8px; 
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        /* Headings usually look better left-aligned even if body is justified */
        text-align: left; 
    }

    p {
        margin-bottom: 12px; 
    }

    .legal-content .font-baumans {
        font-size: 1.05em;
        color: inherit;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .flip-b {
        display: inline-block;
        transform: scaleX(-1);
    }
</style>